est and sue them. The court protects the comatose spouse from potential self-dealing\u2014asset manipulation, unfair settlements, etc.\n\nSo the conscious spouse might remain guardian for care decisions but lose that role for the divorce itself.", "embedding": [-0.02116607129573822, 0.07338966429233551, -0.03407672047615051, 0.00867975503206253, 0.029311906546354294, -0.016549676656723022, -0.0027903662994503975, 0.008666472509503365, 0.10828134417533875, 0.03209763392806053, 0.023819517344236374, 0.051161039620637894, 0.003816266544163227, 0.02678161859512329, 0.06362906098365784, -0.016308976337313652, 0.04850310459733009, -0.04207387566566467, -0.02613139897584915, 0.10825199633836746, -0.016857676208019257, 0.02759336121380329, -0.00624464824795723, -0.03351946175098419, 0.02077876590192318, -0.043094828724861145, -0.0036598555743694305, -0.09709849208593369, 0.01814904808998108, -0.014325248077511787, 0.040642157196998596, -0.06398578733205795, 0.0044472673907876015, -0.0037428236100822687, -0.021944429725408554, 0.07624128460884094, -0.03166808560490608, 0.0676707997918129, -0.08540176600217819, -0.04469776898622513, 0.005818678066134453, -0.013668549247086048, 0.020222578197717667, -0.06612583249807358, -0.045697905123233795, -0.032079316675662994, -0.07101519405841827, -0.00681345583871007, -0.08093267679214478, -0.038310736417770386, -0.15850135684013367, -0.0016461178893223405, 0.033354535698890686, 0.09549576044082642, 0.017406363040208817, 0.020028112456202507, 0.0205887109041214, 0.011839700862765312, -0.0787227600812912, 0.08569905906915665, -0.05949932709336281, 0.039316754788160324, 0.018685409799218178, -0.01412360928952694, 0.04672454297542572, 0.02435397356748581, 0.08092664927244186, -0.01959371194243431, 0.034004781395196915, -0.03499780222773552, 0.024076439440250397, -0.018129698932170868, 0.0648827999830246, -0.04488910362124443, 0.02482645772397518, 0.008022729307413101, 0.025956524536013603, 0.00821236614137888, 0.083727166056633, -0.060286